    "Id": "chassisdef_dengier_DG1-OE",
    "Name": "Dengier",
    "Details": "The DG1-OE configuration is built around Heavy Lasers, pairing two Heavy Large Lasers and two Heavy Medium Lasers with a Targeting Computer for improved accuracy across the board. A Light AC/5 provides ballistic backup and an Active Probe adds battlefield awareness. Nineteen double heat sinks manage the considerable thermal load from sustained heavy laser fire, making this a punishment-focused close-range platform.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
